<br>
I'm not in charge over here, so I don't make announcements like this (/poke Azug).  But I think it's fair to say that many of us have moved on past BG1.<br>
<br>
Myself and many others stayed there for over 2 months.  I capped out in RPs, and got another alt up to level 24 to keep from outleveling people.<br>
<br>
I know many still want to remain in BG1 to cap out as well.  But let me tell ya, getting 1 RP per kill is pretty rough.  Unless you are a stealth class, it's gonna be a long haul.  Come join the rest of us and level to BG3.  My first kill (at level 30 no less) i got 64 RPs.<br>
<br>
And leveling from 24-30 seems fairly quick.  Jeth and I both went from 24-28+ in one night.<br>
<br>
Also, I realize many people are just starting out over here.  I'm willing to help with coinage or whatnot, just let me know.  You should be able to get to level 10 or so quicker on your own than you would with us, but after that, you're welcome to join us if its possible.  <br>
<br>
Only stipulation is if we are deep in someplace please don't expect us to come back and get every person that logs in or that is all we would be doing <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  We will try to find places to xp that are accessible, or at the least announce where we will be beforehand.<br>
<br>
Next Monday we will be hunting the entrance to Spindella.  Bind in Galpien, and check your Mid maps for location.<br>
<br>
